    DatabaseManager
    This class manages the entry data database.

    This class is for showing a DatePickerDialog fragment.
    EditEntryActivity
    Activity for editing existing entry data and updating or removing the data.
    EntryData
    This class contains the entry data.
    ExampleInstrumentedTest
    Instrumented test, which will execute on an Android device.
    ExampleUnitTest

    MainActivity

    MonthlyViewActivity

    MonthlyViewViewHolder

    MyAdapter

    YearlyViewActivity
    Used for displaying the yearly view for the income and expenses entry data.
